(2182, 286606, 'rssmi_item_description', 'a:1:{i:0;a:11:{s:9:"mystrdate";i:1433863833;s:7:"mytitle";s:31:"Get ‘The ASEAN Beat’ in PDF";s:6:"mylink";s:51:"http://www.aseannews.net/get-the-asean-beat-on-pdf/";s:6:"mydesc";s:1598:"<p>BANGKOK, Jun 1 &ndash; Download your PDF copy of the &lsquo;The ASEAN Beat&rsquo; newspaper <a href="http://www.aseannews.net/wp-conte%E2%80%A6/uploads/theASEANBeat2015_WEB.pdf">here</a>! The eight-page newspaper was produced on-site at the Reporting ASEAN media forum held in Bangkok on Mar. 31-Apr 2, 2015.<span></span></p>\n<p>It contains the pick of stories focusing on discussion and debates from the forum, which was attended by more than 100 people and featured parallel sessions, talk-show format discussions and exhibits by cartoonists and illustrators from ASEAN countries on how they see ASEAN as a community.</p>\n<p>The newspaper contains discussions on issues like how to cover ASEAN regionalism more criticall<a href="http://www.aseannews.net/get-the-asean-beat-on-pdf/the-asean-beat/" rel="attachment wp-att-1741"><img title="The ASEAN Beat" src="http://www.aseannews.net/wp-content/uploads/The-ASEAN-Beat-195x300.png" alt="" width="195" height="300"></a>y and beyond the high-profile events, the ASEAN organization&rsquo;s views about how media follow it, and suggestions on how to craft more interesting stories into what is in many ways the region&rsquo;s biggest ongoing story.</p>\n<p>&lsquo;The ASEAN Beat&rsquo; was named such by its editor, Johanna Son, to capture two meanings &ndash; that of the pulse and &lsquo;busyness&rsquo; of an increasingly integrated region, as well as a news beat in traditional media parlance, as journalists need to follow the impact and challenges that the Community may well have on the everyday lives of ASEAN&rsquo;s constituency. (END)</p>";s:7:"myimage";N;s:8:"myAuthor";s:9:"Admin IPS";s:12:"itemcategory";s:114:"Features, Reporting ASEAN: 2015 and Beyond Series, The ASEAN Beat, asean, ASEAN Beat, ASEAN Community, ASEAN media";s:7:"mycatid";s:1:"5";s:7:"myGroup";s:10:"ASEAN News";s:6:"feedID";i:53203;s:13:"useMediaImage";i:0;}}'),
