(19823, 291193, 'rssmi_item_description', 'a:1:{i:0;a:11:{s:9:"mystrdate";i:1409124649;s:7:"mytitle";s:15:"Targeting Asean";s:6:"mylink";s:48:"http://focus-asean.com/sanjay-gupta-focus-asean/";s:6:"mydesc";s:2017:"<h2>Sanjay Gupta, key executive of Aspect Software, assumes the position of<br>\nRegional Vice President for Asean, India and the Middle East<span></span></h2>\n<p>The appointment of Mr. Gupta is with immediate effect and he will relocate from India to work out of Aspect&rsquo;s Asia-Pacific and Middle East (APAC &amp; ME) headquarters in Singapore. In his new role, Gupta will be responsible for driving Aspect&rsquo;s market strategies and go-to-market investments as well as leading the channel partner and alliance engagements.</p>\n<div><img alt="Photo: Supplied by fifthring" src="http://focus-asean.com/pages/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Sanjay-Gupta-274x300.png" width="274" height="300"><p>Photo supplied by Aspect Software</p></div>\n<p>&ldquo;During the past few years, I have been observing Aspect&rsquo;s growth in Asean with great interest. It is an exciting time for the company as we look to strengthen our strategic partnerships and networks to bring Aspect&rsquo;s market-leading interaction management solution as well as workforce and back-office optimisation portfolios further across the region,&rdquo; Gupta said.</p>\n<p>&ldquo;I am thrilled about the opportunities ahead of us and look forward to working with the team,&rdquo; he added</p>\n<p>With a career spanning over 20 years, Sanjay has previously held leadership positions at various reputable companies.</p>\n<p>He furthermore earned degrees from Narsee Monjee Institute, Mumbai, as well as Mysore University.</p>\n<p>Among others, Aspect Software is a provider of cloud solutions, workforce and performance management and multi-channel solutions. The company was founded in 1973 and employs 1,900 people.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div><em>If you would like to inform us of other job changes, email research@focus-asean.com</em></div>\n<p><i>&nbsp;</i></p>\n<p><i>&nbsp;</i></p>\n<p>The post <a href="http://focus-asean.com/sanjay-gupta-focus-asean/">Targeting Asean</a> appeared first on <a href="http://focus-asean.com/">Focus Asean Magazine</a>.</p>";s:7:"myimage";N;s:8:"myAuthor";s:18:"Joana Maria Tacken";s:12:"itemcategory";s:13:"Asean Affairs";s:7:"mycatid";N;s:7:"myGroup";N;s:6:"feedID";i:53105;s:13:"useMediaImage";i:0;}}'),
